  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.poster.avif?t=1758469681\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.webm?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.mp4?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Marco and Eva dive into the pages of colorful comics to rescue animals imprisoned by the evil Glurks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marco</strong> whistles to call for his pet dogs to charge to his aid.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eva</strong> squeezes her pet birds to make them lay explosive eggs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ann</strong> twirls to make her cats pounce.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has 4 breeds to find, unlocking new powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six secondary animals that attack automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to control, with only one action button per character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four chapters and an infinite mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chapters are procedurally generated for maximum action!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The destructible environment allows you to release many monsters tactically, or by mistake, causing panic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your own route: will you free an animal, or will you opt for a much-needed heart to regain some health?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood can be replaced with black ink or white paint. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Little Survivors</strong> is the first game of a solo developer inspired by Franco-Belgian comics such as Asterix, Dungeon, Kid Paddle and Game Over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.poster.avif?t=1758469681\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.webm?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.mp4?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.poster.avif?t=1758469681\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.webm?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/3bee186036deeca1e5d03194b0ceebe1.mp4?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Marco and Eva dive into the pages of colorful comics to rescue animals imprisoned by the evil Glurks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marco</strong> whistles to call for his pet dogs to charge to his aid.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eva</strong> squeezes her pet birds to make them lay explosive eggs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ann</strong> twirls to make her cats pounce.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has 4 breeds to find, unlocking new powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Six secondary animals that attack automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to control, with only one action button per character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four chapters and an infinite mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The chapters are procedurally generated for maximum action!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The destructible environment allows you to release many monsters tactically, or by mistake, causing panic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt your own route: will you free an animal, or will you opt for a much-needed heart to regain some health?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blood can be replaced with black ink or white paint. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Little Survivors</strong> is the first game of a solo developer inspired by Franco-Belgian comics such as Asterix, Dungeon, Kid Paddle and Game Over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.poster.avif?t=1758469681\" width=600 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.webm?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655770/extras/0c88b42f3e306580e3d6f75faa7c0329.mp4?t=1758469681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
